  E' l \<equiv> resets l
"

text \<open>
  Turning around the edges to obtain a single source shortest paths problem.
\<close>
(* XXX Tune for efficiency *)
definition "
  E l \<equiv> if l = n then [0..<n] else filter (\<lambda> l'. l \<in> set (E' l')) [0..<n]
